# Streamlit Dashboard

The project includes an interactive dashboard with:

## Overview

- market snapshot
- latest price
- latest return
- current volatility estimate

## Volatility Models

- model comparison
- RMSE/MAE visualization
- realized volatility vs GARCH forecast

## Risk Analytics

- VaR comparison
- violation analysis
- return distribution

## Model Insights

- quantitative interpretation
- GARCH parameter overview


Run the dashboard:

```bash
streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py
